      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "DEvis is not mentioned in the paper. While the paper does show MA-plots of shrunken vs. unshrunken LFCs (Figures 2 and 3), DEvis as a tool is not discussed.",
