      "asbval:note": "IHW is mentioned in the paper but only in passing as a separate Bioconductor package for hypothesis weighting. It is not presented as a tool directly used in the DESeq2 design specification workflow described in the paper. The card lists it as a tool for 'factor-design-specification' but the paper does not connect IHW to design formula specification\u2014IHW is mentioned in context of p-value adjustment methods, not design specification.",
