      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "IHW is not described in the DESeq2 paper passages provided. The paper does not discuss IHW as an alternative or complementary method. The primary p-value adjustment method discussed is Benjamini-Hochberg with independent filtering.",
