      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We use GLMs with a logarithmic link, log 2 q ij = (cid:2) r x jr \u03b2 ir , with design matrix elements x jr and coefficients \u03b2 ir... Expanded design matrices... In linear modeling, a categorical variable or factor can take on two or more values or levels.",
