      "asbval:source_excerpt": "`apeglm` is the adaptive t prior shrinkage estimator from the \n  [apeglm](http://bioconductor.org/packages/apeglm) package\n  [@Zhu2018]. As of version 1.28.0, it is the default estimator.",
      "asbval:substring_in_paper": false,
