      "asbval:claim_text": "Adding variables to the design can control for additional variation in counts and increase sensitivity for finding differences.",
      "asbval:note": null,
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13059-014-0550-8",
      "asbval:source_excerpt": "By adding variables to the design, one can control for additional variation\nin the counts. For example, if the condition samples are balanced\nacross experimental batches, by including the `batch` factor to the\ndesign, one can increase the sensitivity for finding differences due\nt",
