      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:claim_text": "In experiments with many samples, there will likely be technical variation affecting the observed counts that must be modeled.",
      "asbval:note": "Claim omits that failing to model technical variation leads to spurious results, which is an important qualifier in the source",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13059-014-0550-8",
      "asbval:source_excerpt": "in experiments with many samples\n(e.g. 50, 100, etc.) it is highly likely that there will be technical\nvariation affecting the observed counts. Failing to model this\nadditional technical variation will lead to spurious results.",
